text.tspan: Your orders will always be shipped to the lab listed on your price sheet. This
setting will not change the lab you are sending your order to. Choosing your
lab here allows you to set defaults for orders for your most used lab. If you use
a different lab than your default, these settings will not apply.
Choosing to enable auto-approval of orders allows orders to be
automatically sent to the lab for printing. ShootProof cannot be held liable
The settings below are very important. Learn more about the risks of turning
Auto Approval will send client orders to the lab without your prior approval. Your
settings are very important. Once an order is sent to the lab, it cannot be changed or
canceled. Are you sure you want to turn on Auto Approval?
